paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the impact of KCNH2 gene mutations on long QT syndrome type 2, focusing on heterozygous and homozygous conditions. It provides computational modeling data but does not specify individual genetic variants in KCNH2.

challenges: The paper did not specify individual genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the general effects of KCNH2 mutations without detailing specific variants.
